// @check
// @error An i32-keyed Map isn't supported yet
// DIAGNOSTIC (B6a, BUG 3): a `Map()` annotated with an i32 key (`{[i32]: V}`) is
// the native list/array shape, not the string-keyed hash map. The type checker
// reports the limitation directly rather than letting it become an array and
// fail confusingly. (i32-key Map support is a deliberate follow-up: use `T[]`.)
let m: {[i32]: i32} = Map()
